{"tid":2203753,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林書豪：「我需要離開中國，我哭了。」","createTime":"2020-09-15T14:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T07:29:00.000Z","uid":125434,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"924c4eebfb2829689b54fc05793d7c4866b46d86","tid":2203753,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6Cdv2p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6Cdv2p.png&h=0b90460a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林書豪上個月傳出已取得台灣護照，更宣布自己唔會回歸北京，直言係人生最難嘅決定，用左4星期去諗，甚至諗到失眠。林書豪更話「每日早上4、5點就紮醒，一直諗。雖然首鋼對我好好，但到最後我覺得自己仲有NBA嘅夢想，我仲有時間打，我必須要去追。」<br />\n<br />\n但有消息指係傾唔掂續約金額，所以無續，林書豪仲話自己而家必須離開中國，同家人朋友講起要離開中國，真係喊左出黎，真係辛苦晒啦，書豪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFJ9kb3lqoe/?igshid=1h92iamlbqk4m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFJ9kb3lqoe%2F%3Figshid%3D1h92iamlbqk4m&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=56729887\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFJ9kb3lqoe%2F%3Figshid%3D1h92iamlbqk4m&h=1f863e58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CFJ9kb3lqoe/?igshid=1h92iamlbqk4m</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">祈禱囉偽善撚屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d257e00563b237ef032d17f8c13f4100c732b26","tid":2203753,"uid":52276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"你永遠都係中国人呀！"},{"pid":"f9a0e48dd6bd702a1da2ab793a41f92975fd69fb","tid":2203753,"uid":34869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"開心到哭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557e8bade7cf538d91cd81db431340606be54